aa(lp11
VThere are several scenarios for the future newspaper.
p12
aVSome people say it should be free;
p13
aVit should be tabloid, or even smaller: A4;
p14
aVit should be local, run by communities,
p15
aVor niche, for some smaller groups like business \u2014
p16
aVbut then it's not free; it's very expensive.
p17
aVIt should be opinion-driven;
p18
