aa(lp69
VBut it's not only about the front page.
p70
aVThe secret is that we were treating
p71
aVthe whole newspaper as one piece,
p72
aVas one composition \u2014 like music.
p73
aVAnd music has a rhythm, has ups and downs.
p74
aVAnd design is responsible for this experience.
p75
aVFlipping through pages is readers experience,
p76
aVand I'm responsible for this experience.
